"{\"content\":{\"body\":\"![](https://miro.medium.com/max/1400/1\\\\*62_zY3yV9p_YafikJgL9qw.png)\\n\\nWe are excited to announce that the WePiggy lending protocol builds a strategic partnership with 4EVERLAND, a Web 3.0 infrastructure.\\n\\nThe two parties will jointly explore the Web 3.0 + DeFi fields, including enabling permanent access to the application of WePiggy and a more friendly cross-chain lending experience, etc.\\n\\n4EVERLAND is a Web 3.0 cloud computing platform that integrates storage, computing, and network core capabilities to provide inter-blockchain communication, decentralized front-end, write-once, run any blockchain solutions and web services, enabling developers to build Web 3.0 applications more easily and quickly.\\n\\nWePiggy focuses on building an open-source, non-custodial crypto-asset lending market protocol that helps users realize asset appreciation and maximize utilization across many blockchain networks. On the premise of giving priority to funding security, WePiggy actively creates a more diverse lending market, optimizes the execution efficiency of smart contracts, and expands more dimensions of the business logic. Under the WePiggy multi-chain deployment plan, WePiggy is covering Ethereum, OKExChain, Binance Smart Chain, Polygon, Huobi Eco Chain, Arbitrum, Optimism, Moonriver, Harmony and innovative public and Layer-2 networks.\\n\\n## WePiggy + 4EVERLAND\\n\\n4EVERLAND is committed to providing a new set of IPFS-based front-end deployment and hosting services that enable permanent access to the application of WePiggy.\\n\\nClick [\\\\*here \\\\*](https://wepiggy.me/)to enjoy the “Lite version” of WePiggy lending protocol.\\n\\nSo, based on the superior services of 4EVERLAND, we’re one step closer to a serverless and Web 3.0 application.\\n\\nIn the meantime, WePiggy will promote the widespread use of 4EVERLAND, through its high-quality DeFi community.\\n\\nTo 4EVERLAND, WePiggy will participate in the ecological construction of 4EVERLAND’s official Web3.0 as an outstanding partner.\\n\\n***“Through this integration, our enhanced security solution \\\\[Ark operation\\\\] will be more complete and will further eliminate the risks caused by users being unable to access the front-end. Also, as 4EVERLAND‘s outstanding partner, this will bring WePiggy more display opportunities, greater influence, and greater adoption in the 4EVERLAND community.”***\\n\\n**– Ron, Zheng, Founder of WePiggy**\\n\\n## About WePiggy\\n\\nWePiggy is an open-source, non-custodial, crypto asset lending market protocol. In WePiggy’s market, users can deposit their crypto assets to earn interest, or borrow other crypto assets by paying interest. WePiggy aims to spread the benefits of cryptocurrency’s freedom and transparency to the widest possible user community in a more friendly and simple way, as well as be a good partner for them in wealth management.\\n\\n**[Website](https://wepiggy.com/)**\\\\*\\\\* | **[Twitter](https://twitter.com/wepiggydotcom)** | **[Medium](https://wepiggy-com.medium.com/)** | **[Forum](https://gov.wepiggy.com/)** | **[Discord](https://discord.gg/pew9k58)** | **[Github](https://github.com/WePiggy)** | \\\\*\\\\***[Telegram](https://t.me/wepiggy)**\\n\\n## About 4EVERLAND\\n\\n[4EVERLAND](https://www.4everland.org/) is a Web3.0 cloud computing platform that integrates storage, computing and network core capabilities. 4EVERLAND is committed to providing a distributed, highly efficient, self-motivated, and low-cost data hosting gateway that hopes to help the internet to make a smooth leap from Web 2.0 to Web 3.0, and become the infrastructure for millions of Web 3.0 developers and applications.\\n\\n**[Website](https://www.4everland.org/)**\\\\*\\\\* | **[Twitter](https://twitter.com/4everland_org)** | **[Telegram](https://t.me/org_4everland)** | **[Discord](https://discord.com/invite/Cun2VpsdjF)** | **[Reddit](https://www.reddit.com/r/4everland/)** | \\\\*\\\\***[Medium](https://4everland.medium.com/)**\",\"timestamp\":1641545261,\"title\":\"WePiggy Reaches Partnership with 4EVERLAND In Web3.0\"},\"digest\":\"10Sc3HIuMJ_vByMUlF56Be8hPxZvNwdyD2bpWd--zIg\",\"authorship\":{\"contributor\":\"0xf14a9FA917a5517867e4e0018f320c1F6BF6f182\",\"signingKey\":\"{\\\"crv\\\":\\\"P-256\\\",\\\"ext\\\":true,\\\"key_ops\\\":[\\\"verify\\\"],\\\"kty\\\":\\\"EC\\\",\\\"x\\\":\\\"N058fbF2oH-5FRUnNLTMyeE3rf-G_BHzR0C8oeW7Iq0\\\",\\\"y\\\":\\\"qplgfXXk1tm_RlmpNgaRICzwQ_jygCJmICubkF3Ct8k\\\"}\",\"signature\":\"Wwe-81gHQcXHCR8QxD1EWcyWh_BBQLHduQq-912eAJC98IDmRKa_ptJNbqSiIunavVYqHsiie4HEK8jlRpf4lA\",\"signingKeySignature\":\"0xb09510e4564695a83514694625f4542ed3f53eda5ab968255fe4def27a1d1be57643a01bb6126cf2d95f59f63f7362fabd4919eb5de0046cdad4810ae1f86fef1c\",\"signingKeyMessage\":\"I authorize publishing on mirror.xyz from this device using:\\n{\\\"crv\\\":\\\"P-256\\\",\\\"ext\\\":true,\\\"key_ops\\\":[\\\"verify\\\"],\\\"kty\\\":\\\"EC\\\",\\\"x\\\":\\\"N058fbF2oH-5FRUnNLTMyeE3rf-G_BHzR0C8oeW7Iq0\\\",\\\"y\\\":\\\"qplgfXXk1tm_RlmpNgaRICzwQ_jygCJmICubkF3Ct8k\\\"}\",\"algorithm\":{\"name\":\"ECDSA\",\"hash\":\"SHA-256\"}},\"nft\":{},\"version\":\"12-21-2020\",\"originalDigest\":\"10Sc3HIuMJ_vByMUlF56Be8hPxZvNwdyD2bpWd--zIg\"}"